c0000009
00:02:07.590 --> 00:02:08.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Great.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:08.630 --> 00:02:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the face she makes when
she's hiding something from me.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:14.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've known Mistress Frieren
for a long time.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:14.460 --> 00:02:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing good happens
when she makes that face.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:20.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's plotting to buy
something we don't need.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:22.060 --> 00:02:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Look what I got.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:23.270 --> 00:02:25.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] What are you
going to use that for?</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:25.530 --> 00:02:27.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A corrosive potion that
only dissolves clothing.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:28.070 --> 00:02:29.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Return it!</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. A history tome.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:30.980 --> 00:02:33.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's value in
traditional study.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Well,</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:38.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe that last one
wasn't entirely unnecessary.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Best of luck.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:41.620 --> 00:02:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll meet you
at the inn later.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:43.790 --> 00:02:46.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:47.090 --> 00:02:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:54.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
We can't afford to waste</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:54.810 --> 00:02:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what meager funds we have.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:58.010 --> 00:03:00.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I better keep a
close eye on her.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:00.180 --> 00:03:04.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:04.350 --> 00:03:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
An accessory shop?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:07.230 --> 00:03:08.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[disgruntled sigh]</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:09.570 --> 00:03:11.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You should stop going
to sleep with wet hair.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:13.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Really.
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:15.580 --> 00:03:18.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never thought she would
be interested in fashion.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:18.780 --> 00:03:22.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:23.660 --> 00:03:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She seemed so conflicted.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:27.380 --> 00:03:28.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:28.420 --> 00:03:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that face?</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:31.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In all these years,
I've never seen</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren look
so troubled before.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:35.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water gushing]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:39.050 --> 00:03:40.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:42.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[mewing]</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:48.060 --> 00:03:52.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[coins clinking]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:55.660 --> 00:03:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
She certainly took her time.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:05.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose one accessory
doesn't hurt.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:05.210 --> 00:04:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's better than heavy bones
or strange potions.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:11.830 --> 00:04:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should probably get
back to my own shopping.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:14.580 --> 00:04:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there anywhere I can get
a good dessert in this town?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way. Now she's
taking it too far!</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:21.590 --> 00:04:22.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Try the tavern.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's over in the
basement of that building.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:24.590 --> 00:04:25.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should ask there.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:25.730 --> 00:04:27.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will. Thanks.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] It's been
months since I've even</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:29.100 --> 00:04:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>seen a granule of sugar!</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:31.100 --> 00:04:35.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:36.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales and groans]</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:47.790 --> 00:04:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales and groans]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
This must be the place.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:54.330 --> 00:04:55.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Does
anyone know where I can get</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:56.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a good dessert around here?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:57.010 --> 00:04:58.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clinking]
-Hm...</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:58.220 --> 00:05:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Something tells me this
isn't a pastry loving crowd.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:01.930 --> 00:05:03.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A dessert joint?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:03.630 --> 00:05:05.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you realize who
you're talking to?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:09.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Oh, no.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:09.350 --> 00:05:12.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've stumbled upon the
biggest sweet-teeth in town,</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lucky lady!</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:13.890 --> 00:05:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll find you a
sugar fix, near or far.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:20.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I was not expecting that.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:21.150 --> 00:05:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would've thought you
lot too rugged for sweets.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:25.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A bit of sugar
fills us with the energy</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:25.870 --> 00:05:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we need to adventure on.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:29.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-So they're adventurers, then.
-After a long day's work,</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:29.870 --> 00:05:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still, I'd say "rugged"</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is an understatement.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:33.250 --> 00:05:35.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN]They're terrifying.
-Gotta live a little, right?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:35.090 --> 00:05:36.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:36.170 --> 00:05:37.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hope you enjoy!</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:41.380 --> 00:05:43.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She must be on her way
to the restaurant.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:49.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Huh? That's strange.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:49.270 --> 00:05:51.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's heading in the
direction of our inn.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:51.430 --> 00:05:53.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did she give up on dessert?</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:53.850 --> 00:05:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:54.990 --> 00:05:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not even close
to done shopping.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:00.940 --> 00:06:01.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're late.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:03.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Put down your things.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:12.330 --> 00:06:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rummaging]</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:15.260 --> 00:06:16.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:16.300 --> 00:06:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's been too long
since we've had a treat.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:21.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[seagulls cawing]</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:22.630 --> 00:06:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rustling]</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:23.880 --> 00:06:24.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:27.270 --> 00:06:28.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:34.060 --> 00:06:35.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What an incredible view.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:36.030 --> 00:06:37.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A superb recommendation.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:39.070 --> 00:06:40.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel awful.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:41.150 --> 00:06:43.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was wrong of me
to ever doubt you.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:43.780 --> 00:06:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean?</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:45.660 --> 00:06:46.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:47.450 --> 00:06:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Choose whatever you would like.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:49.870 --> 00:06:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're absolutely
sure we can afford this?</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:52.740 --> 00:06:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have been
saving up in secret.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:57.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
So she is capable of saving.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:02.710 --> 00:07:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What will you order,
Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:05.180 --> 00:07:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:06.430 --> 00:07:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today, I feel like...</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:11.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You feel like Merkur
pudding, right?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[short exclamation]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:12.970 --> 00:07:13.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[short gasp]</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:14.310 --> 00:07:15.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Tonight you feel like</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:15.610 --> 00:07:17.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Merkur pudding, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:17.570 --> 00:07:18.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you know?</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:18.980 --> 00:07:20.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You travel with
someone for years,</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:20.650 --> 00:07:22.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you pick up on things.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:24.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can just tell with you.
[munches]</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:24.320 --> 00:07:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:29.530 --> 00:07:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't tell what any
of you are thinking.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:33.080 --> 00:07:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then we should
put in more effort</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:34.530 --> 00:07:36.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you can get
to know us better.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:36.710 --> 00:07:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My favorite food, for
starters, is a Ruf-omelette.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:39.750 --> 00:07:40.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Mine is grapes.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sourer, the better.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:45.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And mine is--
-[FRIEREN] Booze, correct?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:45.220 --> 00:07:47.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You make that clear,
you corrupt priest.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:49.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is nothing to blush about.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:49.890 --> 00:07:51.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find it disturbing
that your vice</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:53.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a primary
player in our tale.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:55.560 --> 00:07:57.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'm sorry, Fern.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:58.980 --> 00:08:00.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you have
to be sorry for?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:02.020 --> 00:08:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I realized I don't know
the first thing about you,</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I...</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:06.780 --> 00:08:09.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't know what sort of
present you would like.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:12.740 --> 00:08:13.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is for me?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:15.630 --> 00:08:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I completely forgot
it was my birthday.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:21.960 --> 00:08:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exclaims]</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:28.340 --> 00:08:30.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a hair ornament, right?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:30.930 --> 00:08:32.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's absolutely perfect.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:32.930 --> 00:08:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, I love it.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:35.190 --> 00:08:36.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did well?</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:37.230 --> 00:08:38.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very well,</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:38.270 --> 00:08:39.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and because
you're hopelessly dense</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when it comes to these things,</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:41.150 --> 00:08:42.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>allow me to be clear.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:43.850 --> 00:08:46.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am overjoyed that you're
trying to get to know me.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:47.110 --> 00:08:49.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is a gift in itself.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:52.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Simply trying means that much?</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:52.990 --> 00:08:54.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:55.580 --> 00:08:57.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe we should
find you a spell</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:57.290 --> 00:08:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for understanding
people's feelings.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:59.580 --> 00:09:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:04.460 --> 00:09:05.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:06.260 --> 00:09:07.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shutting]</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:09.340 --> 00:09:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Fern.
Are you ready to be off?</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:11.630 --> 00:09:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:13.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[water lapping]
-[fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:13.930 --> 00:09:16.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me the truth, Mistress.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:28.490 --> 00:09:31.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does our journey have a
notable purpose this time?</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:31.990 --> 00:09:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not especially.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:33.530 --> 00:09:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hopefully, we'll be able to
find some decent spells though.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:40.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That, and whenever possible,</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:40.540 --> 00:09:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to retrace
the adventures</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:42.250 --> 00:09:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had with Himmel
and the others.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:45.300 --> 00:09:47.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before all signs of it fade.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:47.550 --> 00:09:48.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:48.670 --> 00:09:50.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Remembering those adventures?</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:50.420 --> 00:09:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's very important
to you, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:57.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That's what I want to find out.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:57.810 --> 00:09:59.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:03.100 --> 00:10:05.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems you've finally
grown taller than me.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:06.690 --> 00:10:08.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I am 16.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:08.530 --> 00:10:10.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could be your big sister.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:10.690 --> 00:10:12.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that right?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:12.940 --> 00:10:16.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our diets are largely the same,
so that can't be the culprit.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How strange.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:25.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[hawk cawing]</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:40.100 --> 00:10:41.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whirring]</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:42.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:43.470 --> 00:10:47.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:52.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your defensive training
is coming along nicely.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, let's put your
work to the test.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:58.660 --> 00:10:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[zaps]</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:07.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:10.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I aimed for the
gaps in your magic.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:13.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If this were a real fight,
you'd be dead</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:13.880 --> 00:11:14.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:15.430 --> 00:11:17.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How will you
handle it this time?</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:17.970 --> 00:11:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:20.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With no gaps.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:20.970 --> 00:11:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:22.970 --> 00:11:24.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And this time?</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:24.970 --> 00:11:27.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:28.070 --> 00:11:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing]</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:31.190 --> 00:11:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:33.610 --> 00:11:35.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is plenty for today.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:36.370 --> 00:11:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water gushing]</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:43.870 --> 00:11:45.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Defensive magic is powerful,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:46.040 --> 00:11:48.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it rapidly
depletes your mana.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maintain defense
over a large area,</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:51.290 --> 00:11:53.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you'll exhaust
your supply in seconds.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:55.300 --> 00:11:56.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Meaning that the best option</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:56.720 --> 00:11:58.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to cast it in
select locations</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:58.680 --> 00:12:00.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the precise
moment of impact.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:00.430 --> 00:12:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Exactly.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:08.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:13.770 --> 00:12:14.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[straining]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:17.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:17.910 --> 00:12:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been practicing
nothing but defense for ages.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:20.700 --> 00:12:22.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, to improve
your odds of survival.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:24.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess that makes sense</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:26.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being able to cast
one defensive spell</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:28.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can protect you from
most every offensive spell.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:29.250 --> 00:12:31.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's eerie
how powerful they are.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:31.330 --> 00:12:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So,</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:35.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you haven't read the tome
on magical history I gave you.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:35.970 --> 00:12:39.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic is just as much about
theory as it is about practice.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:40.470 --> 00:12:41.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:41.800 --> 00:12:43.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You leave me no choice
but to read it to you</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:43.890 --> 00:12:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at bedtime every night.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:45.850 --> 00:12:47.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll read it myself.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:49.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I'm not a child anymore.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:00.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is this village so special?</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:03.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just another place
to find spells, right?</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:03.410 --> 00:13:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, unfortunately not.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:06.290 --> 00:13:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eh, it's all up to
the weather, now.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That it is.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Could one of you gentlemen
help us? -Hm?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:12.710 --> 00:13:13.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 3B]
It's an elf.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:13:14.210 --> 00:13:15.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That hair.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:13:17.510 --> 00:13:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you happen to be the mage
that they call Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:13:21.180 --> 00:13:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:22.300 --> 00:13:23.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you know that?</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:24.590 --> 00:13:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:25.690 --> 00:13:28.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're here to see the place
where Qual was sealed.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:30.060 --> 00:13:31.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll show you the way.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:33.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Qual?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:34.310 --> 00:13:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Elder Sage
of Corruption, Qual.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:37.860 --> 00:13:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 2A]
He's a horrific demon,</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:39.610 --> 00:13:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>responsible for
the many atrocities</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:41.780 --> 00:13:43.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that befell this region.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:44.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About 80 years ago,</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:44.570 --> 00:13:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel the Hero
and his party sealed him away.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:47.660 --> 00:13:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:50.210 --> 00:13:51.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That seal doesn't
have much time left,</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:52.040 --> 00:13:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm here to defeat him
before he's an issue.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:56.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where does your
information come from?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:57.470 --> 00:13:59.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't recall telling
anyone about this.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:14:00.420 --> 00:14:02.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until about 30 years ago,</b></Default>

c0000262
00:14:02.720 --> 00:14:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel always
went out of his way</b></Default>

c0000263
00:14:04.470 --> 00:14:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to pay our town
an annual visit.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:14:07.350 --> 00:14:10.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He told me it was to check
on the condition of the seal.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:14:11.020 --> 00:14:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was always
rather soft at his core.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:14:13.680 --> 00:14:17.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were a frequent subject
of conversation between us two.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:19.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We agreed
you were quite heartless</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:19.280 --> 00:14:20.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for not checking on him.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:22.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
She's a touch cold.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:23.030 --> 00:14:24.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. And then some.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:24.650 --> 00:14:26.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Sorry about that.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:26.540 --> 00:14:27.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still...</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:28.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she's not so heartless</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she'd leave
your village to its fate.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:31.540 --> 00:14:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When the seal is on the verge
of collapse, she'll appear.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:35.920 --> 00:14:38.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it would seem he was right.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:39.260 --> 00:14:40.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:48.220 --> 00:14:49.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is it?</b></Default>

c0000279
00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was right to assume
that it's unstable.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:15:06.620 --> 00:15:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall dispel the
seal tomorrow,</b></Default>

c0000281
00:15:08.950 --> 00:15:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then take care of Qual.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:15:11.540 --> 00:15:13.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crickets chirping]</b></Default>

c0000283
00:15:17.670 --> 00:15:19.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were the one who
thought to seal him away</b></Default>

c0000284
00:15:19.710 --> 00:15:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the first place,
weren't you?</b></Default>

c0000285
00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:23.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't you
and the others defeat him</b></Default>

c0000286
00:15:24.050 --> 00:15:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you had the chance?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:15:25.970 --> 00:15:29.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The story isn't as enthralling
as you might guess.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:31.930 --> 00:15:32.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:33.100 --> 00:15:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I couldn't beat him.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:37.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All the Demon King's
forces were formidable,</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:37.940 --> 00:15:40.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but Qual was
an exceptional mage.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:40.610 --> 00:15:42.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He developed Zoltraak,</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:42.610 --> 00:15:45.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the first piercing spell
in the history of magic.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:46.700 --> 00:15:48.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can pierce
not only defensive spells,</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the most durable
magic resistant armors.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:52.330 --> 00:15:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It directly targets
and destroys the body.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:55.790 --> 00:15:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is said that
in this region,</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:58.420 --> 00:16:00.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>40 percent of their adventurers</b></Default>

c0000299
00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and 70 percent of their mages
were killed by Zoltraak.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:16:04.630 --> 00:16:05.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000301
00:16:07.760 --> 00:16:10.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A spell with that much
power shouldn't exist.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:16:10.510 --> 00:16:12.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Agreed. As would most.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:16:13.050 --> 00:16:14.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was too strong.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:15.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:16:15.430 --> 00:16:18.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it was that strength that
caused it to backfire on him.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:21.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean, backfire?</b></Default>

c0000307
00:16:21.560 --> 00:16:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:28.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's painfully clear that you
haven't read your history tome.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:28.740 --> 00:16:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sure you don't need
nightly bedtime stories?</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll start reading now.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't. It's fine.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:35.750 --> 00:16:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's more important that
you get a good night's sleep.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] You'll see
for yourself tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:48.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm dispelling the seal.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:48.890 --> 00:16:50.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mustn't let
your guard down.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:58.980 --> 00:17:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind blowing]</b></Default>

c0000318
00:17:02.230 --> 00:17:03.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[hissing]</b></Default>

c0000319
00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:09.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:17:20.830 --> 00:17:24.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Long time, no see, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:27.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How many years has it been now?</b></Default>

c0000322
00:17:27.930 --> 00:17:28.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eighty.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:17:29.300 --> 00:17:32.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No time at all, then.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:17:32.720 --> 00:17:34.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For us, perhaps not.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:17:35.600 --> 00:17:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's become
of the Demon King?</b></Default>

c0000326
00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We killed him.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:17:39.810 --> 00:17:41.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:43.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then,</b></Default>

c0000329
00:17:43.600 --> 00:17:46.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall avenge his death.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:17:46.450 --> 00:17:48.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern...cast a defensive spell.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:17:50.070 --> 00:17:53.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zoltraak!</b></Default>

c0000332
00:17:53.990 --> 00:17:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0000333
00:18:00.250 --> 00:18:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh? What have we here?</b></Default>

c0000334
00:18:03.830 --> 00:18:06.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You blocked Zoltraak.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:18:06.420 --> 00:18:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That defensive spell of yours
must be powerful indeed.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:18:12.170 --> 00:18:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000337
00:18:13.920 --> 00:18:16.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you please tell me
what's going on?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:19.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was ordinary
offensive magic.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:18:20.310 --> 00:18:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just saw his life's work.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:18:22.850 --> 00:18:25.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to introduce
you to Zoltraak.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:27.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The great killing
magic of legend.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:18:28.820 --> 00:18:29.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:18:31.990 --> 00:18:33.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Qual,</b></Default>

c0000344
00:18:33.320 --> 00:18:35.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your spell was
simply too powerful.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:18:37.540 --> 00:18:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
After you were sealed away,</b></Default>

c0000346
00:18:39.580 --> 00:18:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>mages across the land</b></Default>

c0000347
00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>studied and analyzed Zoltraak</b></Default>

c0000348
00:18:43.080 --> 00:18:45.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until they had a complete
understanding of it.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:18:46.380 --> 00:18:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In just a few years,</b></Default>

c0000350
00:18:48.050 --> 00:18:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your work was incorporated
into humankind's magic system,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:51.800 --> 00:18:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and new defensive spells</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:53.510 --> 00:18:56.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with power like none before,
were developed in response.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:58.180 --> 00:19:00.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The magic resistance
offered by equipment</b></Default>

c0000354
00:19:00.220 --> 00:19:02.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has improved
significantly as well.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:19:02.850 --> 00:19:04.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These advances
have made Zoltraak</b></Default>

c0000356
00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a death sentence no longer.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:19:07.690 --> 00:19:10.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your great weapon is now
"ordinary offensive magic."</b></Default>

c0000358
00:19:12.360 --> 00:19:13.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:19:14.030 --> 00:19:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's rather remarkable
how much humanity</b></Default>

c0000360
00:19:16.240 --> 00:19:18.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can achieve
in a span of 80 years.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:19:18.830 --> 00:19:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Qual...</b></Default>

c0000362
00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:22.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you don't resist, I'll
grant you a painless death.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:19:24.040 --> 00:19:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's interesting.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I see what you've done.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:19:28.550 --> 00:19:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your defense attunes
itself to my magic,</b></Default>

c0000366
00:19:31.840 --> 00:19:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then disperses its power.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:19:34.380 --> 00:19:37.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have
a complex spell indeed.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:19:37.760 --> 00:19:38.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0000369
00:19:38.970 --> 00:19:42.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must consume
a great deal of mana.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:45.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He figured out the
weakness of defensive magic.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:19:45.560 --> 00:19:47.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Fern...you
know what to do, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:19:48.860 --> 00:19:51.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Yes. I remember
from our practices.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:52.610 --> 00:19:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'm going to ask
that you protect me as well.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:56.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[zaps]</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:56.700 --> 00:19:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:58.450 --> 00:19:59.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[zapping]</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:00.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0000378
00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

c0000379
00:20:15.760 --> 00:20:16.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000380
00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh? The elf can fly?</b></Default>

c0000381
00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:24.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How fun.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:20:25.510 --> 00:20:27.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zoltraak.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:20:36.780 --> 00:20:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren...</b></Default>

c0000384
00:20:38.530 --> 00:20:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that spell</b></Default>

c0000385
00:20:40.370 --> 00:20:43.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is mine.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:20:44.030 --> 00:20:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000387
00:20:54.040 --> 00:20:55.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Thank you, Frieren.
-You saved our town!</b></Default>

c0000388
00:20:55.970 --> 00:20:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000389
00:21:00.010 --> 00:21:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of you,
our quiet village</b></Default>

c0000390
00:21:01.800 --> 00:21:03.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can live in peace once more.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:21:04.050 --> 00:21:05.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000392
00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:06.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen that hat.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:21:07.020 --> 00:21:08.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This old thing?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:21:09.940 --> 00:21:11.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Around these parts,</b></Default>

c0000395
00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the sun beats down
on us all year long.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:21:14.020 --> 00:21:15.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every farmer has one.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:21:16.410 --> 00:21:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen this one.
This exact straw hat.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:21:25.660 --> 00:21:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You!</b></Default>

c0000399
00:21:27.040 --> 00:21:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the little delinquent
who flipped up my skirt!</b></Default>

c0000400
00:21:30.750 --> 00:21:31.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aha!</b></Default>

c0000401
00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Have you got a
death wish, you brat?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:38.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been wanting
to do that for ages,</b></Default>

c0000403
00:21:38.260 --> 00:21:40.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But unlike you,
I have self control.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:21:40.340 --> 00:21:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
You better not kill him.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:21:41.470 --> 00:21:42.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Calm yourself,
and I'll allow you</b></Default>

c0000406
00:21:42.930 --> 00:21:45.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-a peak up mine instead.
-Gross.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:21:45.260 --> 00:21:46.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:21:49.310 --> 00:21:51.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're still alive, then.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:21:51.730 --> 00:21:55.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to your visit, I'll
be able to live even longer.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:21:55.810 --> 00:21:57.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad I trusted
Himmel's words</b></Default>

c0000411
00:21:57.860 --> 00:21:59.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and waited for you to come.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000413
00:22:03.490 --> 00:22:06.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000414
00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saved them.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:22:11.790 --> 00:22:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They all seem so thankful.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:22:14.040 --> 00:22:16.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thankful, yes, but not to me.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:22:17.300 --> 00:22:19.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His prophecy came to pass.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:22:19.130 --> 00:22:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel is who they believed in.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:22:22.420 --> 00:22:24.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't understand exactly.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:26.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it seems to me</b></Default>

c0000421
00:22:26.350 --> 00:22:27.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the person
Himmel believed in</b></Default>

c0000422
00:22:27.930 --> 00:22:29.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all this time was you.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:22:31.270 --> 00:22:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:22:34.390 --> 00:22:35.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it, Mistress?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:22:36.320 --> 00:22:37.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:22:37.530 --> 00:22:39.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000427
00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Because I felt sorry for you.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:24:21.710 --> 00:24:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] She was
rather irresponsible.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:24:23.460 --> 00:24:24.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] It's no time
for such depressing talk!</b></Default>

c0000430
00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:26.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
It happened a long time ago.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:24:26.220 --> 00:24:28.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME]
I now know it as Aureole,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:24:28.300 --> 00:24:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the land where souls rest.</b></Default>

